,Not Recommended,269210,13681442,"Posted: 28 December, 2014",all,Phyrebat,"Gotta say the fact that something as essential (Essential for this kind of game anyway) as MULTIPLAYER is a payed for DLC is utter nonsense.I repeat! You Have to BUY ONLINE MULTIPLAYER as a seperate DLC. I see now why ""Multiplayer"" isn't included in the tags.Now, on to my (admitttedly limited) experience with the game:It was okay I guess. Nothing really grabbed my attention. The graphics were nice enough, the controls worked, the enemies kind of wandered towards me as I kited them all to death with little trouble at all. I found that my abilities had trouble acitvating however. Many times I'd press the button (even 2 or 3 times) and nothing would happen. The ability icon would be in full colour, but it just wouldn't activate.Eventually I reached the first boss and that's where this games shortcomings really brought themselves out. The boss was this armless zombie who spawned swarms of flies and threw giant spike balls. Sounds interesting in concept, but the execution was rather poorly done.1) The swarms of flies are constantly moving towards me which results in a constant wall between me and the boss and he always spawns more as soon as I clear a swarm.2) The flies each have a noticable amount of health. They are not as easy to clear as you'd think flies would be.3) Every time he attacked, And I do mean EVERY TIME he attacked, the boss would speak one of his 3-4 sayings. And with his neverending wall of flies you can imagine that those lines would get repetitive.4) Eventually the flies started spawning with elemental enhancements which didn't seem like a problem at first, until one fly touched me and I was frozen and then instagibbed by the swarms.5) I levelled up like, 7-10 times just on those flies alone, in like, a few minutes. To me there's something wrong with a boss fight if the minions He's spawning are strong enough to warrant that much of a reward.TLDR: 1) Visuals and music are nice2) Controls work for the most part3) You have to BUY ONLINE MULTIPLAYER4) Bosses can be frustrating to fight5) Character sayings get annoying6) Can't shoot diagonally7) Get's pretty old really fast"
