er) levels. I still don't enjoy the way this game was rebalanced so I am leaving my review as is, but for anyone who cares: if you are willing to be extremely patient as you grind out ♥♥♥♥♥♥ deaths over and over, the game does eventually appear to be playable again, at least for a while (presumably until the stage you're on outlevels your gear)."
